Dan. <ets>kok</ets> heap, or E. <ets>cock</ets> to set erect.]</ety>
<def>A small conical pile of hay.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cock</ent>⟦br⟧

