hay.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Under the <qex>cocked</qex> hay.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cock</ent>⟦br⟧

